{"title":"【旅行】常州天目湖二日游","date":"2020-08-22T01:00:00.000Z","date_formatted":{"ll":"Aug 22, 2020","L":"08/22/2020","MM-DD":"08-22"},"thumbnail":"/images/travel/changzhou/tianmuhu_bg.jpg","link":"2020/08/22/20200823_travel_changzhou","comments":true,"tags":["Travel"],"categories":["旅行"],"updated":"2020-08-28T07:39:30.507Z","content":"<h2 id=\"规划\">规划<a title=\"#规划\" href=\"#规划\"></a></h2>\n<h3 id=\"时间\">时间<a title=\"#时间\" href=\"#时间\"></a></h3>\n<p>2020/08/22 09:00 ～ 2020/08/23 21:30</p>\n<h3 id=\"路线\">路线<a title=\"#路线\" href=\"#路线\"></a></h3>\n<figure class=\"highlight plain\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">2020&#x2F;08&#x2F;22 │ 南京站 → 溧阳站 → 万达广场 → 酒店</span><br><span class=\"line\">2020&#x2F;08&#x2F;23 │ 酒店 → 天目湖景区 → 溧阳站 → 南京站</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n<h2 id=\"车票\">车票<a title=\"#车票\" href=\"#车票\"></a></h2>\n<h3 id=\"南京站-→-溧阳站\">南京站 → 溧阳站<a title=\"#南京站-→-溧阳站\" href=\"#南京站-→-溧阳站\"></a></h3>\n<p><img src=\"/images/travel/changzhou/ticket_01.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"φcx\"></p>\n<p><img src=\"/images/travel/changzhou/liyang_01.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"φcx\"></p>\n<h2 id=\"酒店\">酒店<a title=\"#酒店\" href=\"#酒店\"></a></h2>\n<h3 id=\"锦江都城酒店\">锦江都城酒店<a title=\"#锦江都城酒店\" href=\"#锦江都城酒店\"></a></h3>\n<p>地点：溧城镇平陵中路268号<br>\n评分：★★★☆</p>\n<p><img src=\"/images/travel/changzhou/hotel_02.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"φcx\"></p>\n<p><img src=\"/images/travel/changzhou/hotel_01.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"φcx\"></p>\n<h2 id=\"美食\">美食<a title=\"#美食\" href=\"#美食\"></a></h2>\n<p>常州这边的特色是砂锅鱼头、扎肝、白芹还有地皮菜等等</p>\n<h3 id=\"相遇（溧阳万达广场店）\">相遇（溧阳万达广场店）<a title=\"#相遇（溧阳万达广场店）\" href=\"#相遇（溧阳万达广场店）\"></a></h3>\n<p>这家店的装修很有特色，然后菜品的话推荐剁椒鱼头和猪手</p>\n<p><img src=\"/images/travel/changzhou/food_xiangyu_01.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"φcx\"></p>\n<p><img src=\"/images/travel/changzhou/food_xiangyu_02.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"φcx\"></p>\n<p><img src=\"/images/travel/changzhou/food_xiangyu_03.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"φcx\"></p>\n<p><img src=\"/images/travel/changzhou/food_xiangyu_04.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"φcx\"></p>\n<p><img src=\"/images/travel/changzhou/food_xiangyu_05.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"φcx\"></p>\n<h3 id=\"唐老鸭大酒店\">唐老鸭大酒店<a title=\"#唐老鸭大酒店\" href=\"#唐老鸭大酒店\"></a></h3>\n<p>在天目湖景区边上，点的都是特色菜，老板人还行，打八折</p>\n<p><img src=\"/images/travel/changzhou/food_tanglaoya_01.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"φcx\"></p>\n<p><img src=\"/images/travel/changzhou/food_tanglaoya_02.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"φcx\"></p>\n<p><img src=\"/images/travel/changzhou/food_tanglaoya_03.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"φcx\"></p>\n<p><img src=\"/images/travel/changzhou/food_tanglaoya_04.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"φcx\"></p>\n<h2 id=\"景点\">景点<a title=\"#景点\" href=\"#景点\"></a></h2>\n<h3 id=\"天目湖\">天目湖<a title=\"#天目湖\" href=\"#天目湖\"></a></h3>\n<p>今天天气不错，没有下雨，天气也不是特别热。我们买了快艇+游船+观光车的套票，景区内湖水清冽，水质纯净，群山环抱，峰峦绵亘。我们今天正好赶上演出，so happy ≧ω≦ 山水园景区分为湖里山、龙兴岛、茶岛，进园后直接到游船码头乘船到龙兴岛。</p>\n<p><img src=\"/images/travel/changzhou/tianmuhu_01.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"φcx\"></p>\n<p><img src=\"/images/travel/changzhou/tianmuhu_02.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"φcx\"></p>\n<p><img src=\"/images/travel/changzhou/tianmuhu_03.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"φcx\"></p>\n<p><img src=\"/images/travel/changzhou/tianmuhu_04.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"φcx\"></p>\n<p><img src=\"/images/travel/changzhou/tianmuhu_05.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"φcx\"></p>\n<p><img src=\"/images/travel/changzhou/tianmuhu_06.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"φcx\"></p>\n<p><img src=\"/images/travel/changzhou/tianmuhu_07.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"φcx\"></p>\n<p><img src=\"/images/travel/changzhou/tianmuhu_08.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"φcx\"></p>\n<p><img src=\"/images/travel/changzhou/tianmuhu_09.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"φcx\"></p>\n<p><img src=\"/images/travel/changzhou/tianmuhu_10.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"φcx\"></p>\n<p><img src=\"/images/travel/changzhou/tianmuhu_11.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"φcx\"></p>\n<p><img src=\"/images/travel/changzhou/tianmuhu_12.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"φcx\"></p>\n<p>最后附一张可爱的老婆</p>\n<p><img src=\"/images/travel/changzhou/miaomiao_01.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"φcx\"></p>\n","next":{"title":"【旅行】扬州一日游","link":"2020/07/11/20200711_travel_yangzhou"},"plink":"https://shome.love/2020/08/22/20200823_travel_changzhou/","toc":[{"id":"规划","title":"规划","index":"1","children":[{"id":"时间","title":"时间","index":"1.1"},{"id":"路线","title":"路线","index":"1.2"}]},{"id":"车票","title":"车票","index":"2","children":[{"id":"南京站-→-溧阳站","title":"南京站 → 溧阳站","index":"2.1"}]},{"id":"酒店","title":"酒店","index":"3","children":[{"id":"锦江都城酒店","title":"锦江都城酒店","index":"3.1"}]},{"id":"美食","title":"美食","index":"4","children":[{"id":"相遇（溧阳万达广场店）","title":"相遇（溧阳万达广场店）","index":"4.1"},{"id":"唐老鸭大酒店","title":"唐老鸭大酒店","index":"4.2"}]},{"id":"景点","title":"景点","index":"5","children":[{"id":"天目湖","title":"天目湖","index":"5.1"}]}]}